---
import HQShell from '../layouts/HQShell.astro';
---
<HQShell title="AlphaTag Arsenal" active="arsenal">
  <section class="hero"><div class="hero-grid"><div><div class="kicker">Equipment Briefing</div><h1>AlphaTag Arsenal</h1><p>A public-safe overview of the Laserwar AlphaTag training platform used inside the Zombie Patrol arena. This page should stay guest-facing and avoid operational/security details.</p></div><img class="hero-logo" src="/assets/logos/alphatag-logo.png" alt="AlphaTag" /></div></section>
  <div class="panel-grid">
    <section class="panel span-4"><h2>Training Hardware</h2><p>Describe packs, tags, sensors, and game roles at a guest level.</p></section>
    <section class="panel span-4"><h2>Scenario Systems</h2><p>Explain team play, objectives, respawns, healing, and scoring without exposing configuration details.</p></section>
    <section class="panel span-4"><h2>Annelle Records</h2><p>AlphaTag game exports become public-safe training records only after Annelle import and filtering.</p></section>
  </div>
</HQShell>
